@@TJvImageListViewer
<TITLEIMG TJvImageListViewer>
JVCLInfo
  GROUP=JVCL.Graphics.Static
  FLAG=Component
Summary
  Control that displays the images from an image list.
Description
  Use TJvImageListViewer when you need to display the images from an image list in a grid like
  control.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageListViewer.Images
Summary
  Lists images available for items in the TJvImageListViewer.
Description
  Images is a list of bitmaps that can be displayed for each item in the TJvImageListViewer. Each item
  in the control displays the image corresponding to the item's index in the control.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageListViewer.OnGetCaption
Summary
  Called when the control needs to get the caption to use for an item.
Description
  Write a handler for the OnGetCaption event when you want to provide captions for the items in a
  TJvImageListViewer.
Parameters
  Sender     - The object that triggered the event.
  ImageIndex - The index of the image in the image list to provide a caption for.
  ACaption   - The caption to draw along with the image.

