@@TJvImageListViewerOptions
Summary
  Options class for the TJvImageListViewer control.
Description
  TJvImageListViewerOptions is the class used for the Options property of a TJvImageListViewer. It
  derives from TJvCustomItemViewerOptions and publishes many of its properties as well as introducing
  new ones.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageListViewerOptions.DrawingStyle
Summary
  Specifies the style to be used when an item is drawn.
Description
  Use the DrawingStyle property to control how an item is to appear. DrawingStyle controls how much of
  the blend color specified by the image list's BlendColor is combined with the foreground, or what
  background color to use.
See Also
  TJvImageListViewerOptions.SelectedStyle

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageListViewerOptions.FillCaption
Summary
  Specifies whether the background of captions are filled in their entirety or not.
Description
  Use FillCaption to specify whether the background of the caption of an item is filled in such a
  manner that the fill extends from the left to the right edge. If FillCaption is false, only the area
  covered by the caption is filled.

  FillCaption only affects selected items.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvImageListViewerOptions.SelectedStyle
Summary
  Specifies the style to be used when a selected item is drawn.
Description
  Use SelectedStyle to specify the style to use for selected items.
See Also
  TJvImageListViewerOptions.DrawingStyle

